        <systemModelName xml:lang="en">Allocation, cut-off by classification</systemModelName>
        <samplingProcedure xml:lang="en">Industry data, representative 100 % of European (EU-28) production capacity, based on production volumes in 2018.

The industrial data used originate from five different MDI producers with six plants, in five European countries.</samplingProcedure>
        <extrapolations xml:lang="en">This dataset has been copied from an original dataset covering the geography RER. The uncertainty has been adjusted accordingly.

An exchange representing unreacted raw materials that are recycled to the process after treatment, with a representation of 5.6% on dry mass output, was cut-off.

</extrapolations>
